{{Italic title}}
'''''Leela Charitra''''' is a biography of Bhagavan Shri [[Chakradhar Swami]], the guru of the [[Mahanubhava]] sect, and is a sacred text of that sect.<ref>{{cite book |title=Indian Literature |last=Nagendra |year=1988 |publisher=Prabhat Prakashan |oclc=19812121 |page=205 |location=Delhi }}</ref>  It was written in the late 13th century by his follower [[Mhaimbhat]].<ref>{{cite book |title=Knit India Through Literature |last=Civacaṅkari |year=1998 |publisher=Eastwest Books |isbn=978-81-88661-15-2 |page=131 }}</ref>  It is the earliest known written work of [[Marathi language|Marathi]] literature. "Leela Charitra" Latest Edition will be published in the year 2016 by Raghav bhat satarkar

