The Roman Catholic Church in [[Albania]] is composed of : * two Roman Catholic [[ecclesiastical province]]s, comprising two Metropolitan Archdioceses and three Suffragan dioceses * one pre-diocesan jurisdiction of the [[Italo-Albanian Catholic Church]], a [[particular church]] ''sui iuris'' using the [[Byzantine Rite]] [[Albanian language]], comprising only a single [[Apostolic Administration]].
